flowchart TD
    A([Model in Production]) --> B[Monitoring Layer]

    B --> C{Drift or\nAnomaly Detected?}

    C -- No --> D[Ongoing Metrics Tracking\nAccuracy - Fairness - Latency]
    D --> B

    C -- Yes --> E[Diagnosis]

    E --> F{Drift Type?}

    F --> G[Input Drift\nData distribution shift]
    F --> H[Concept Drift\nInput-label relationship evolved]
    F --> I[Label Drift\nTarget variable redefined]

    G & H & I --> J[Escalation Protocol\nNotify - Triage - Assign Owner]

    J --> K{Severity Level?}

    K -- Low --> L[Targeted Tuning\nFeature refresh or threshold adjustment]
    K -- Medium --> M[Retraining Assessment\nNew data - Validation - Versioning]
    K -- High --> N[Rollback or Freeze\nExecutive notification]

    L & M --> O[Experimentation Loop\nTest hypothesis - Validate on subgroups]
    N --> O

    O --> P[Model Review\nBusiness alignment - Regulatory fit - Fairness audit]

    P --> Q{Model Still Fit\nfor Context?}

    Q -- Yes --> R[Redeploy Updated Model]
    Q -- No --> S[Sunset Protocol\nDocument - Archive - Retire]

    R --> B
    S --> T([Lifecycle Closed\nInstitutional Knowledge Preserved])

    style A fill:#1e3a5f,color:#fff
    style T fill:#1e3a5f,color:#fff
    style C fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style F fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style K fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style Q fill:#2d6a9f,color:#fff
    style J fill:#c0392b,color:#fff
    style N fill:#c0392b,color:#fff
    style S fill:#7f8c8d,color:#fff